wiki.summary: “JACKBOYS” is an instrumental track produced by superproducer Mike Dean alongside WondaGurl, who set the tone for the album with synths and a powerful distorted vibe. The 48-second track develops a melody growing in volume and clarity, which then transitions into and becomes the intro of “GANG GANG.” The track was originally titled “INTRO” on streaming services before being changed to “JACKBOYS” a day after release. Read more on Last.fm.
